"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"I can’t get around the most obvious aspect of crypto generally which is that it’s hard.  So far the obstacles for normal people are pretty serious.  I’m going to try and collect and share what I learn on my own journey and hope it helps others as they come on board the web3 train.  I don’t know where this is going or headed but the more I try to learn and read the deeper the hole seems to be …\\n\\nHard to say where to really start, but I was thinking about a domain, a blog, twitter etc … the usual starter kit and thought instead I should work with an existing web3 provider for the time being so [mirror.xyz](https://mirror.xyz) it is for now.\\n\\nAlright so a few concepts off the bat I will explore immediately and try to keep it as simple as possible for everyone who might stumble in …\\n\\n* Blockchain\\n* web3\\n* Cryptocurrency\\n* NFTs\\n* metaverse\\n\\nThese are all hopefully obvious but as soon as you start to dig in I’m sure there will be questions or blockers preventing more basic knowledge for more people.  I am quite certain there will be more to explore beyond the core here today … so let’s begin!\",\"timestamp\":1638214842,\"title\":\"Simple crypto and web3\"},\"digest\":\"6wVymdTcsClMQqBFi6eudDB-KqMr52L8p46rYtPJdUg\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x994f606aD8862A135dbA43974F7Bf702275ea6B8\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"QWbVaWv2f0yxWKw4iKRVdflhBeF5TRfY9WzSY6ZkwZg\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"hK5douw_1pvjV8gmSMQacMYnW5PqG0CCOr-hjqSS908\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"NnzH7sEPzD6g4QB-fD03IFzKC795bAND88YldjxzCS5rW7MynlG6ml9AcVN6n5dgSjtEElZXoQFjvb126wTGHQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc2280b29bf99e58aaadcf59a6a4272b2e38a6d19ba5694e23b2337d059924af97172a38eac8c8df32ec9f95d2363e845f059d429fd2becd61fb3251075e07ef01b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\